reviewText: Wonderfully hilarious performance with a serious moral. Why, oh why is this not yet available on Blu-Ray or DVD? My VCR player is now gone.
I really enjoyed Tartuffe.  It was clear and I could hear the sound very well. The tape was in excellent condition.
This is an excellent version of this classic comedy. It is a filmed play on a set. It isn't for everyone, but if you are familiar with the story, this version does it justice.
